{"tid":1466833,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[置頂] 和理飛814","createTime":"2019-08-13T16:57:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-14T07:42:36.000Z","uid":69314,"like":55,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":54,"replies":[{"pid":"f0c78bb01567fc2d9964ca7c928e89aa7c850a70","tid":1466833,"uid":69314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:57:24.000Z","msg":"錯就要認，但呢一次仲有機會<br />\n<br />\n聽日繼續和理飛<br />\n<br />\n應承我 以下既野<br />\n<br />\n1. 不打人<br />\n<br />\n2. 不捉鬼<br />\n<br />\n3. 不衝禁區<br />\n<br />\n4. 不要帶頭和和應他人衝擊<br />\n<br />\n5. 無視想帶頭搞事人群<br />\n<br />\n6. 不要幫拖還手<br />\n<br />\n7. 不受傷<br />\n<br />\n8. 有可疑人物搞事搵機場保安出手<br />\n<br />\n機場係今次運動最重要既地方，勝敗靠佢，你睇呢2日政府做左幾多野去破壞機場既集會，我地要做既野只係用人數去癱瘓，而唔係周圍捉鬼同起哄，比你捉到都無用，一陣文宣又輸，見到其他既現象請無視，以人數靜坐至癱瘓，機場重點在有機場特警，而不是狗。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">運動尚未完結，請繼續出黎<br />\n今天的失利是為了明天的努力</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"a06010c7f2af65ff8e72a8f69fc9f51efb88fabe","tid":1466833,"uid":69314,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:57:50.000Z","msg":"612"},{"pid":"1b98ca6f114cd45c1f02f1f538e01a1c64bc53a8","tid":1466833,"uid":69314,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:58:12.000Z","msg":"721"},{"pid":"4ca03e4a70115552c5049c2dfb27701cf668ca95","tid":1466833,"uid":69314,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:58:22.000Z","msg":"812"},{"pid":"627e51a4fff4b69be1f762a5dc5549ca38cc72a3","tid":1466833,"uid":33543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:58:29.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ac724b59a25528af4b24725e160316b456cb23d0","tid":1466833,"uid":69314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:59:10.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"83f042190a479c1583afee9a66fd06e3b3ef650b","tid":1466833,"uid":238275,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:59:19.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: green;\">推推推 不斷學習改進 變強</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"b9c8fdaedf08f58541be7ed25938a288fca5afcd","tid":1466833,"uid":238275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:59:32.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: green;\">推推推 不斷學習改進 變強</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75f611a70475b8afc02008db61e546c2f3d77eac","tid":1466833,"uid":52574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:59:37.000Z","msg":"從來都唔係【癱唔癱】既問題，而係【如何癱】既問題<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1464999\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1464999</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n求大家睇下同投個票<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n今晚係轉捩點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ca071e17fab629337c9c4a920888082751128b5","tid":1466833,"uid":69314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:01:06.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3f352e0a0b4cc3d68de3a89cc80ce43e17f2949a","tid":1466833,"uid":5253,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:01:16.000Z","msg":"「示威者在這兩個月來真是疲於奔命，很多休息時間都沒有，其實真是很辛苦。我們有時都要體諒，有時那一刻電光火石，影響判斷，有時出現誤中，都是不以為奇的事情。」<br />\n<br />\n「今日機場行動，唔完美，可接受，但需要改善、改進。」"},{"pid":"364fadfd20f27cb430caa91aac5a827a29d17a8a","tid":1466833,"uid":69646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:01:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b7d13a1797754eea8920f683467ccff2cf5e6617","tid":1466833,"uid":238275,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:01:50.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: green;\">推推推 </span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"80cb66fc91cfc877dea