k\">https://lih.kg/1466733</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">不要被仇恨支配自己</span></span>"},{"pid":"7b5d8d9caa354e8c2b489164ea02036f86a19817","tid":1466833,"uid":21170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:31:11.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n<br />\n順手推自己個post<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n經過今晚我有少少嘢想講，跪求所有勇武和理巴絲入嚟<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1467520\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1467520</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"d2c3b840ca3135e4ac454ecc23def39034410971","tid":1466833,"uid":135222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:31:40.000Z","msg":"跟咗 聽日真係無死<br />\n唔該大家"},{"pid":"d6ac913ff477c4eaf052db54a82d76c233aec2a4","tid":1466833,"uid":66221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:32:29.000Z","msg":"推吓先"},{"pid":"1b00333fa1f5a3c57f60a4377b3db8432347c22b","tid":1466833,"uid":236646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:32:30.000Z","msg":"聽日道歉🙇"},{"pid":"b1258d3263dbfc15114b12881e3a10b9cef3eb58","tid":1466833,"uid":66221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:33:06.000Z","msg":"但係聽日駛唔駛要大家一齊去道歉？"},{"pid":"ded4ac688a2bf0ae3b8707de158c6561c0166091","tid":1466833,"uid":66221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:34:30.000Z","msg":"唔該大家可以諗下天琦呢句說話，諗下大家仲欠缺咗乜野<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SxPaHk8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSxPaHk8.jpg&h=4671f666&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d675ea549dd7bd76252926c05550db186409b1aa","tid":1466833,"uid":63311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:35:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db42f91d22c38fc04eb8ecd8fbed1165a7f9e764","tid":1466833,"uid":69314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b1258d3263dbfc15114b12881e3a10b9cef3eb58","tid":1466833,"uid":66221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:33:06.000Z","msg":"但係聽日駛唔駛要大家一齊去道歉？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:35:23.000Z","msg":"不阻止，不反對，兄弟爬山，各自修行"},{"pid":"5f0f0788a842e305f98823d1f9a462f4421fb036","tid":1466833,"uid":300697,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:35:46.000Z","msg":"如需國際輿論協助抗爭，千萬不要再 Block T2！<br />\n以及動粗強行阻擋旅客(特別是西人)登機！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n香港國際機場客運量極大，T2 的狹小不能夠處理一半以上的乘客出入境。Delay 的班機每天一定過百。大量旅客不能順暢登機，飛機好難順利凖時起飛。佔用了停機位，抵港航班延誤是難以避免的。<br />\n<br />\n只佔據T1，旅客一方面覺得有登機的機會，但另一方面需要付出額外的時間代價。他們是會覺得港府無能力與市民對話解決紛爭，而不是覺得示威者暴力。<br />\n<br />\n香港不同其他地方，我們只有一個國際機場。如果我們將它完全癱瘓，只會令許多外國人有家歸不得而對示威者有極大的抱怨。西方國家領袖都是很著緊輿論和選票。如果香港示威者的行為損害到他們國民的權利，他們不會再支持香港示威者。<br />\n<br />\n走到來機場這步棋，已經是最後的對決。8.11 警方是錯得離譜，國際輿論全部都指責警方的暴行。要蓋過一單黑材料，最容易的方法是製造一單更大的黑材料。今天示威者比較霸道的行為完全是正中下懷。<br />\n<br />\n你可能覺得我是P 牌無資格講野，但是千萬不要忘記我們的行動是代表全香港相信抗爭的人。請大家一定要用理智思考如何處理這件事情，不要起於情緒化。<br />\n<br />\n如果你看過這篇文章，無論如何請幫推和 re post , 我絕對不介意你們自行修改，改成你們的意見。<br />\n<br />\n大家加油！"},{"pid":"c52bb662af314ad1e499c656d89279500ac7921b","tid":1466833,"uid":69314,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d675ea549dd7bd76252926c05550db186409b1aa","tid":1466833,"uid":63311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:35:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:36:19.000Z","msg":"其實唔洗理佢 ，咁樣最無引，一陣捉錯人，比人反話轉頭就唔好"},{"pid":"82125b27182268463a7e4cf0f00dee18b99a30c2","tid":1466833,"uid":151313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:38:42.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a2725c5ffe795e00a2de04e89254f4e1141f6c4a","tid":1466833,"uid":151313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:38:56.000Z","msg":"唔玩cancel 玩<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">delay</span></span></strong>!!<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1464220\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1464220</a><br />\n<br />\n屌你地老母 你地有無搭過飛機架？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1464168\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1464168</a><br />\n<br />\n機場現時既建議方法，希望多人睇到<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1464007\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1464007</a><br />\n<br />\n8.13機場策略<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1463429\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1463429</a><br />\n<br />\n延伸閱讀：機場人流<br />\n<br />\n[和你飛] 外國人旅遊，中國人滯留<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1463771\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1463771</a><br />\n<br />\n離境大堂被阻外國人：應該控制，而唔係阻止登記<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1463192\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1463192</a>"},{"pid":"7d7e7c2d73e6b9f8c32d5b79e0ecc27c50351620","tid":1466833,"uid":82413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:38:57.000Z","msg":"721"},{"pid":"30d6b393e420c1666e244a75f7b523d8bca0cbe4","tid":1466833,"uid":69314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:39:16.000Z","msg":"推"}]}